fields.title: Catan
fields.description: In Catan, players try to be the dominant force on the island of Catan by building settlements, cities, and roads.

fields.title: Ticket to Ride
fields.description: Ticket to Ride is a cross-country train adventure where players collect cards of various types of train cars that enable them to claim railway routes connecting cities.

fields.title: Pandemic
fields.description: In Pandemic, players work as a team to treat infections around the world while gathering resources for cures.
